rComments: Simply the best! An inspiring lecturer. A man of class and intergrity. A man of keen wit and joie de vivre.  In your lectures and labs, we felt like part of a large extended family. WE mattered to YOU....and, YOU mattered to US.

Desser is, without a doubt, the best prof I have ever had. While he is serious in his expectations of students, he is a lot of fun to listen to and his love of the subject material is infectious. It's too bad that more professors aren't like him!
serious, demanding but fair teacher... concerned about his students, passionate about the subject matter and overall good guy

The most amazing professor I've ever had in my 3 yrs at this university. He is brilliant, funny, and draws you into the subject matter. He's kind and helpful and he takes the time to learn who you are. It's a shame he's Emeritus.
